# Pure Java Migration - CreateClaim Procedure

Analyzing the RPG procedure `CreateClaim`, I will generate a complete Pure Java application with layered architecture. This procedure processes claim position data from HSGPSLF3, aggregates values by failure number, and creates claim failures in HSG73PF.

**Key Business Logic:**
- Reads position data (HSGPSLF3) grouped by failure number
- Aggregates material (MAT), labor (ARB), and special (other) values
- Identifies maintenance work and part numbers
- Creates failure records in HSG73PF via `createFail` procedure
- Updates claim status in HSG71PF
- Handles text lines (up to 4)

**Architecture:**
- 3 entities: Claim (HSG71PF), ClaimError (HSG73PF), ClaimPosition (HSGPSLF3)
- Repository layer with Spring Data JPA
- Service layer for business logic
- DTOs for data transfer
- Enums for status codes and position types

---

